"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"UTD.htm?3/53/3923?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Health risks of obesity (The Basics)",
"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"UTD.htm?3/55/3954?source=see_link\">",
